  --GTYPE-group-format  # format GTYPE input groups with GFMT
    tested: "--GTYPE-group-format" "input.txt" "other.txt" in formatted_standard
    | flag removes 31 lines: 1,27c1,2, < first line, < second line with trailing spaces, < 	indented with tab, <     indented with spaces
    | exit: 1 → 2
    | stderr: diff: unrecognized option '--GTYPE-group-format'
    without flag:
      1,27c1,2
      < first line
      < second line with trailing spaces
      < 	indented with tab
      <     indented with spaces
      < 	 	mixed tabs and spaces
